OL,3,CBon Jovi on major throat surgery and
OL,4,Cputting their mental health first
OL,6,FJon Bon Jovi tells ITV News' Rishi
OL,7,FDavda that his throat surgery was
OL,8,F'successful' and he 'can sing again'
OL,9,Fbut he's still unsure whether his
OL,10,Fvoice will be strong enough to tour
OL,12,FBon Jovi are a long way from the big
OL,13,Fhair and "bras" of the 1980s - the
OL,14,Frockers are focusing on their mental
OL,15,Fhealth and recovering from throat
OL,16,Fsurgery.
