OL,3,CBon Jovi on major throat surgery and
OL,4,Cputting their mental health first
OL,6,FThe iconic voice of Jon Bon Jovi was
OL,7,Falmost no more after he had to undergo
OL,8,Fmajor throat surgery around two years
OL,9,Fago, but the singer is determined
OL,10,Fhe'll be belting Living on a Prayer
OL,11,Fwith his usual vigour.
OL,13,F"It's eight o'clock in the morning
OL,14,Ffolks, I don't know if you want me to
OL,15,Fhit the high Cs right now, but the
OL,16,Foperation was a success and now it's
OL,17,Fall about recovery," he jokes during a
OL,18,Fsit down interview with ITV News
OL,19,FEntertainment Reporter Rishi Davda.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/8
