OL,3,CBon Jovi on major throat surgery and
OL,4,Cputting their mental health first
OL,6,FHe said: "It's like an athlete, you
OL,7,Fare back at training.
OL,9,F"After the recovery period it's about
OL,10,Ftraining, so just to be clear, I don't
OL,11,Fwant anyone to misconstrue this, I can
OL,12,Fsing again, now the bar is two and a
OL,13,Fhalf hours a night, four nights a
OL,14,Fweek, and then we'll go out on the
OL,15,Froad."
OL,17,FHis journey to recovery is a key part
OL,18,Fof the new four-part documentary Thank
OL,19,FYou, Goodnight: The Bon Jovi Story,
OL,20,Fwhich premiers on Disney Plus on April
OL,21,F26.
