OL,3,CBon Jovi on major throat surgery and
OL,4,Cputting their mental health first
OL,6,FThe series follows the group's journey
OL,7,Ffrom four teenage friends to global
OL,8,Fsuperstars.
OL,10,FHis bandmates drummer Tico Torres and
OL,11,Fkeyboard player David Bryan, who are
OL,12,Fsat either side of him during the
OL,13,Finterview, are also putting their
OL,14,Fhealth first.
OL,16,FThe group admitted they almost
OL,17,F"disbanded" in the early 90s as they
OL,18,Fwere completely "overworked".
