OL,3,CBon Jovi on major throat surgery and
OL,4,Cputting their mental health first
OL,6,FTorres said: "We would go and do 260
OL,7,Fshows, come off the road and in three
OL,8,Fmonths do a record, come back on the
OL,9,Froad.
OL,11,F"It was just this hamster wheel. It
OL,12,Fwas Jon, that brought in a gentleman,
OL,13,Fa mediator that put us in a room
OL,14,Ftogether to talk because it was a
OL,15,Fpoint when we were just so disbanded
OL,16,Fbecause we were so overworked.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/8
