OL,3,CBon Jovi on major throat surgery and
OL,4,Cputting their mental health first
OL,6,F"The fact that we were able to talk to
OL,7,Feach other in an honest presence and
OL,8,Fgo 'this is what I feel and this is
OL,9,Fwhat I feel' and we were kind of able
OL,10,Fto work it out and stay together.
OL,12,F"He was corporate therapist I would
OL,13,Fsay, it really helped us because I
OL,14,Fthink we wouldn't be here today. "
OL,16,FWhile the group say discourse around
OL,17,Fmental health is a key change they've
OL,18,Fgone through in 40 years as a band,
OL,19,Fthey say fashion is another huge
OL,20,Fdifference.
