OL,3,CBon Jovi on major throat surgery and
OL,4,Cputting their mental health first
OL,6,F"We were told what to wear a lot of
OL,7,Ftime, hey wear those parachute pants,"
OL,8,FTorres said.
OL,10,FBryan added:" In the first video for
OL,11,FRunaway I wore a bra thing and I only
OL,12,Fbought it because it was 500 bucks, my
OL,13,Fcar was 100 dollars. It was the most
OL,14,Fexpensive thing I owned at the point.
OL,16,F"See you can laugh at it. You have to
OL,17,Flaugh at it.," says Torres.
OL,19,FJokingly Bon Jovi said: "Otherwise
OL,20,Fyou'd cry, we'd have to call the
OL,21,Fshrink back."
